snippet.title: Do It Whenever?
snippet.description:
DIW - Do It Whenever

Maker, designer, and creator working on various projects and ideas that solve issues while helping others along the way.

3d printing, laser cutting/engraving, software/hardware integration, and brute force garage work are aspects present in my projects and art.

www.thingiverse.com/doitwhenever/designs
www.doitwhenever.com
www.instagram.com/do.it.whenever
